# Admin Assistant

Admin Assistant is a desktop application for managing SSH-accessible servers,
storing reusable scripts, running commands/scripts across hosts, and attaching
AI-assisted troubleshooting workflows to execution history.

This repository currently contains the initial MVP scaffold only. Business
logic-heavy areas such as SSH execution internals, AI provider integrations,
and orchestration details are intentionally left as stubs.

